Body: Our CEO(Anton Zapolskyi) is trader with 10 years experience on The New York Stock Exchange and CME Group.  So, our product was originally developed for own needs. But later we decided to create a perfect ecosystem for the best of ProTraders. To do that Traders should have a trade toolset that perfectly fit their needs and trade assets to unleash full potential of their  trading skills. That why we created Tradelize. We know that traders face multiple challenges while trading cryptocurrencies. These include a lack of professional trading tools, a different and at times incompatible functionality of crypto exchanges and difficulties related to following and quickly reacting to value-creation events.

Body: Hi! No, this project is not about exchange  Our ecosystem consists of 3 synergistic components: 1) Tradelize.web with its Tradelize.score (a service for investors); 2)Tradelize.terminal (solution with easy and accessible interface for trading); 3)Tradelize.brokerage V2.0 (a suite of services for both investors and traders);

Author: mokovelll
Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: Here, sir, is where you are wrong  Coinigy is Web-based platform, which is quiet slow and does not have all those customization features and tools to trade fast and conveniently. Also, can you imagine professional trader working via web-based application, let‚Äôs say on a laptop? It is not efficient, not professional, and quiet absurd, as I see it. ProTraders need at least 3 screens to monitor all data they need to make weighted decisions. It is impossible to customize Web solutions in a way to do so. That is why only software solution can be applied here, not Web.  As for Blockchain Terminal, I say: First of all, Blockchain Terminal is focused on institutional investors only. They are not aiming such markets as independent private companies and retail traders. They do not have instruments for them at all. Secondly, Blockchain Terminal is not free and charge a really high prices for usage of it (thousands of dollars). Finally, our terminal is an instrument and just one of our three products. Our global goals differ dramatically, therefore we are not even competitors, because our global goal is to attract professional traders from mature markets and trading companies, to make crypto trading mass adoption easy and profitable, giving an opportunity to enter this market for housewives, doctors, teachers, students and etc, without leaving behind existing crypto holders. Blockchain Terminal goal is institutional trading: banks and etc. That‚Äôs it

The exact nature of the participation of these parties will be contingent upon the expected government regulation in crypto trading.  We believe the introduction of new regulations is a reason to be optimistic about the future of the crypto economy as a whole and Tradelize in particular. It will allow a large group of new users to flood the market.  For these reasons, our team has decided to move the public sale to a time after official regulations have been announced at the end of June. The public sale is now planned for 15 July, 2018. Author: vicklank

Author: mokovelll
Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: 1) In our project, it is not necessary to connect exchanges through the API - it will only be enough to create an account in our system. There will be an account on which all transactions will be consolidated. By combining transactions through one account on each exchange, we believe that we can get the most profitable fees and transfer these savings to you by offering lower tariffs for each bargain. To act as a custodian for our users, we will get a license. Your money will be placed on the exchange accounts of our system. No one will have direct access to your funds except us, and we could access the funds that you deposited on the platform for copying transactions. (It is also possible to connect to the API).  2) The use of block in our system will allow you to record all the statistics of traders, which guarantees 100% transparency of the performance of traders. Also, each trader will have to trade for two months through our terminal before the investor can subscribe to it.  3) Our product for investors Tradelize.Web will allow not only to follow the trader in an automatic mode, but also the opportunity to trade itself will be available. It will be possible to manage the portfolio, that is, on the one hand, you can view traders' portfolios, and on the other - use extensive settings for risk management, adjust the amount allocated for trader copying and / or strategy and ranges of allowed price execution for copying transactions (trades, which repeat the execution of the trader and / or strategy).  4) Our system will also provide an algorithm creation function for automatic trading along with tools that will help you create your own bot.  5) Our project is designed for three types of audience: a trader, an investor, and a newcomer in the crypto-currency world. Thus absolutely any person can be a participant of cryptology. This will attract a new audience, which in these markets has not yet worked. This will make crypto-economy more healthy. This will also bring additional liquidity, which in general will have a positive impact on the market.  6) Our trading terminal can be customized at the request of the trader. It was developed by traders for traders.  Features of our terminal: 1) A few clicks can be found in the liquidity window with the liquidity depth of the stock exchange or the market. 2) Manage and track all orders from one window 3) The arbitration window will allow to find inefficiency of the market and to earn on them 4) The Positions window will allow you to monitor the performance of your portfolio 5) WatchList will help to keep up to date on the movements of selected crypto-currency assets 6) Ability to add hot keys and newsfeed, as well as charts (graphics) 7) Ability to resolve transactions directly by clicking on the chart (graph) A wide range of risk management settings 9) All sorts of cryptopairs 10) Ability to split the terminal into several screens

Author: mokovelll
Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: The internal referral system is unique in a sense that the inviter does not receive a one-time fee, but the 10% of our income from the users' work in the system during the first year! And he can continue to receive such income from the popularization of the service. For example, the person will invite 1000 users to the system. Each of them will spend on commissions on average $50 USD per month. Thus, all summed up he will receive $50*10%*12*1000 = $60000 USD per year. Such payments will be made in our tokens (they will be redeemed to make a payment) with a grace period of one month. In addition, the system provides for the freezing of tokens in the equivalent of $100 USD and the presence of the additional tokens in the accounts to pay for services. Thus, the referral system working through the token will always exceed the demand for purchase than for sale!

Author: mokovelll
Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: Speaking about practical actions taken towards achieving our goals, we have already done a lot with a product, which is now in the process of testing.  Attempts to unite various exchanges in one terminal were made, but all were limited to poor-made solutions, where there were no real professional tools.  We also made a unique decision to attract professional traders to our platform - 80% of the collected funds will be allocated to them for management at 50% commission (the amount of funds per each of such traders will be up to 500 thousand dollars).  But it seems to us that it is much more important to talk about the ideological side of our project.  The project is aimed at attracting a new audience to crypto trading, which has not yet worked on this market. This will make crypto-economy more healthy. This will also bring additional liquidity, which in general will have a positive impact on the market.  The new audience will consist of players such as private trading companies, who now do not have either technical or risk management tools that allow them to enter the market. Professional traders with extensive trading experience in traditional markets, bringing with them huge capital.  In addition, the project is aimed at making smart mass adoption of cryptoworld. We want the broad masses of the population to enter the market with the help of our functionality and they will be able to get results comparable to the results of professionals. A student, a housewife, a taxi driver, a hairdresser, a doctor - all of them will be able to invest and trade in the crypto currency market, using exclusively our application.  Also, we do not forget about the huge existing market of holders of crypto-currencies, who have the means, but not the knowledge and skills. That is why, we want to create for them the opportunity to multiply their funds by repeating the actions of others.  It is overall description, but still very short  I hope you share our enthusiasm and believe in the crypto-currency economy, as well as the desire to develop it, creating new products and useful things.

During the token sale period, the top ranks of Tradelize.score will start to be filled with the best ProTraders, who will be provided with up to $500K to manage in order to create the best successful strategies for the users. Funds allocated with the best 300 ProTraders will be redistributed on a monthly basis according to their current ranking positions. Any interested trader can connect their accounts on exchanges to Tradelize.score through Tradelize.terminal or directly through API and start using the platform to build their personal Tradelize score. After completion of all the legal formalities and technical procedures the funds will be released from the escrow account and distributed among the 300 best ProTraders and the liquidity pool as follows (provided that the TGE hard cap has been reached): TOP 10: $500–ö each TOP 11-50: $100–ö each TOP 51-100: $75–ö each TOP 101-300: $40–ö each

Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: Hello! As soon as the trader places order, encrypted information lands on the Tradelize server. Copycatting of traders actions is going on our servers.  And then orders sent through a secure channel to the exchange where the transactions takes place. Author: mokovelll
Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: The security system was developed under the guidance of cryptography experts, meaning your funds and data will be reliably protected. Critically important data includes users‚Äô personal data (including KYC data), API keys and secret keys to connecting user accounts to exchange wallets. This data is stored in a separate and completely secured database inaccessible to the public and extranet and only available to the platform‚Äôs internal services. Data stored in this database is partially encrypted while being transmitted within the system upon the internal request. In addition, HTTPS is used as a measure to prevent host spoofing and traffic surveillance while this data is being transmitting between servers within the system. If the monitoring system detects an attack attempt, the database containing critically important data is blocked for 24 hours for any reading and recording, which makes it inaccessible to servers.

Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: You need to register at our platform, where you can participate in the TGE and its stages, deposit funds, buy Tradelize tokens, and find all the necessary information. Next, you need to process with KYC procedures and fund your account. You will be able to withdraw your tokens to a third-party wallet only upon TGE completion. Payment methods include several cryptocurrencies (BTC, ETH). After purchasing the tokens, you will be able to bring them to your ETH wallet (it should be your personal wallet, exchange wallets can't be used). When you pay with cryptocurrencies, a commission fee (transaction fee) is charged by the infrastructure of the corresponding block, the size of which you set yourself, and the transaction speed depends on the congestion of the network and the amount of the commission fee that you set

At least 2 months of trade performance statistics will need to be stored on Tradelize.score before successful traders will be eligible to enter its top ranks. During the token sale period, the top ranks of Tradelize.score will start to be filled with the best ProTraders, who will be provided with up to $500K to manage in order to create the best successful strategies for the users. Funds allocated with the best 300 ProTraders will be redistributed on a monthly basis according to their current ranking positions. Any interested trader can connect their accounts on exchanges to Tradelize.score through Tradelize.terminal or directly through API and start using the platform to build their personal Tradelize score. After completion of all the legal formalities and technical procedures the funds will be released from the escrow account and distributed among the 300 best ProTraders and the liquidity pool as follows (provided that the ICO hard cap has been reached): TOP 10: $500–ö each TOP 11-50: $100–ö each TOP 51-100: $75–ö each TOP 101-300: $40–ö each  Best traders would want to use our platform, because we believe that there's a huge number of traders looking for a professional trading terminal to utilize their skills to full extent. Good news are that we provide it free of charge and also give an opportunity to multiply their profits just by allowing others to follow their trades And to get the very best of them we will allocate 80% of funds raised, for them to share with you their best strategies!  To choose which trader to copy there will be extensive information on each trader‚Äôs statistics available, such as: historical risk, drawdown of the account, trading activity, wines, currency allocation, and risk indicators such as sharp and others.  So it is up to you to decide what is best for you personally and on this basis choose the trader you want to follow.  I hope, that this answer satisfy you üòâ

Author: mokovelll
Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: Tradelize.terminal architecture: 1. Exchange server 2. Exchange API 3. Terminal server 4. Client App When the user places his order, encrypted information lands on the Tradelize.me server. Then it's sent through a secure channel to the exchange where the operation takes place. The main advantage of the architecture is that it allows for the processing of queries at an extremely high velocity while not overloading the exchange API. Thus, everyone using the terminal can be reassured that the operation will be processed instantly. Also, Tradelize.me architecture makes it possible to effectively use complex order-placing schemes - an indispensable option for both professional traders and beginners.

Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: Hello! Thank you for your question  To choose best traders we will held kind of a competition for traders. At least 2 months of trade performance statistics will need to be stored on Tradelize.score before successful traders will be eligible to enter its top ranks. During the token sale period, the top ranks of Tradelize.score will start to be filled with the best ProTraders, who will be provided with up to $500K to manage in order to create the best successful strategies for the users. Funds allocated with the best 300 ProTraders will be redistributed on a monthly basis according to their current ranking positions. Any interested trader can connect their accounts on exchanges to Tradelize.score through Tradelize.terminal or directly through API and start using the platform to build their personal Tradelize score. After completion of all the legal formalities and technical procedures the funds will be released from the escrow account and distributed among the 300 best ProTraders and the liquidity pool as follows (provided that the ICO hard cap has been reached): TOP 10: $500–ö each TOP 11-50: $100–ö each TOP 51-100: $75–ö each TOP 101-300: $40–ö each  Best traders would want to use our platform, because we believe that there's a huge number of traders looking for a professional trading terminal to utilize their skills to full extent. Good news are that we provide it free of charge and also give an opportunity to multiply their profits just by allowing others to follow their trades And to get the very best of them we will allocate 80% of funds raised, for them to share with you their best strategies!  To choose which trader to copy there will be extensive information on each trader‚Äôs statistics available, such as: historical risk, drawdown of the account, trading activity, wines, currency allocation, and risk indicators such as sharp and others. So it is up to you to decide what is best for you personally and on this basis choose the trader you want to follow.  I hope, that this answer satisfy you üòâ

These include a lack of professional trading tools, a different and at times incompatible functionality of crypto exchanges and difficulties related to following and quickly reacting to value-creation events.  Tradelize and its Terminal for trading is here to solve these problems. One of our goals is to provide comprehensive tool set for traders. We think that traders should have a trade toolset that perfectly fit their needs and trade assets to unleash full potential of their  trading skills. So Tradelize.terminal is the first revolutionary DMA (Direct Market Access) standalone software solution with most innovative features from mature capital markets for trading on major global cryptocurrency exchanges. Handcrafted by traders for traders with understanding. It is a solution that installs on the computer and allows you to reach the maximum speed in trading. And finally, it allows to review the necessary markets and currency pairs simultaneously on different monitors.

Title: [ANN] [PRESALE] Tradelize üìà Your Laser Sword In Cryptocurrency Trading
Body: Hello! We want to make the best professional trading tool where pro-traders and trading investors will be able to locate all the required information from all the exchanges of interest in one place. Trading terminal is suitable for individual traders, trading groups as well as large funds for portfolio management facilitation. Here's tools we currently provide: Liquidity depth overview on major crypto exchanges which helps ProTrader to get insight and foresee major changes in prices -Custom price display -Ability to observe all trades, profits and balances in one fiat or cryptocurrency -All crypto exchange balances in one place -Arbitrage trading -Full interface customization -Wide range of risk management settings for individual and corporate usage -SMART orders - a tool that allows to pick the best execution price and liquidity major crypto exchanges have to offer -E-mail, sound and text notifications -Comparative tables for prices on all exchanges, in all currencies -Sorting function for all crypto pairs (by prices, volumes, amounts) -Internal filters HIGH, LOW, Best% change, by volatility and by liquidity allow the trader to keep their finger on the pulse of market volatility -Multi-screen terminal -Connect wallets from different crypto exchanges -All news feeds in one place -Order book allows traders to see bids and offers in a convenient exchange and at any depth -If the trader does not possess any verified accounts on exchanges, they can open an account in Tradelize.brokerage, bypassing time-consuming exchange authentication  By the way, what options are you talking about?
